	<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年，市经信委深入学习党的十八大、十九大和习近平总书记</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">系列重要讲话精神，认真落实市委市政府一系列部署，坚持把服务经济、建设廉洁高效的党员干部队伍作为全委党建工作的首要任务，坚持把</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><A href="http://www.gwyoo.com/lunwen/sxzz/sxzh/"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none" lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>思想</SPAN></SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">政治理论学习作为全委党建工作的坚实基础，坚持把激发党组织活力作为全委党建工作的重要目标，不断增强党组织的凝聚力、战斗力和影响力，为争创昆山市经济和信息化发展新优势提供坚强的思想、组织和作风保证。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">一、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">坚持理论武装，学习型党组织建设不断深化</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">一是常态化制度化推进</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">两学一做</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">学习教育。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">通过组织理论学习、召开理论研讨会、观看《将改革进行到底》等电教片，集中上党课等形式</SPAN><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm" lang=EN-US>,</SPAN><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">不断增强大家理论自信和制度自信，真正做到认识上一致、政治上同心、思想上统一、行动上同步。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二是认真开展党员冬训活动。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">成立冬训活动领导小组，及时制订《经信委冬训工作实施意见》、《深入开展</SPAN><SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">创新四问</SPAN><SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">活动的实施意见》等文件。下发了《习近平总书记系列重要讲话读本》、《关于新形势下党内政治生活的若干准则》等材料，要求全体党员干部撰写学习笔记和心得体会。活动中共撰写了四篇</SPAN><SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">创新四问</SPAN><SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">的专题调研报告。组织青年干部积极参加市级机关青年干部大讲堂，一位青年干部上台开讲并获批优秀讲师。</SPAN><SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">三是认真抓好党的十九大精神的学习贯彻。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">把学习贯彻党的十九大精神作为首要政治任务，作为政治必修课，切实在学深、悟透、做实上下功夫。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">第一时间在委党政联席会议上传达学习十九大精神，委内各支部积极行动，安排专门时间、列出专题，进行集中学习研讨，同时根据市委组织部的要求，迅速落实</SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">八个一</SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">活动，确保各项学习活动有安排、有步骤，并取得预期成效。</SPAN><B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">四是持续推进学习型机关建设。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">制定《创建学习型机关三年实施意见》，以政治理论、经济知识、法律法规、科技知识、文化知识、业务知识为学习重点，通过建立经信学堂、启动交流论坛、开展读书比赛、调研活动、编写场景式服务清单等方式，</SPAN><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">将集体学习和自学结合起来，将座谈和交流结合起来，坚持理论学习与实际工作相结合，引导干部在深刻理解党的最新理论成果的新思想、新观点、新论断的基础上，牢固树立正确的世界观、人生观、价值观，准确把握政治方向，把新精神、新要求贯穿于工作之中。在机关内部营造了人人向学的氛围，不断提高干部职工的思想道德素质和为民服务意识，进一步增强干部职工的理想信念。</SPAN><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">二、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">坚持服务中心，服务型党组织建设不断深化</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">一是</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">认真开展</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">六个一</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: 0.2pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">基层走访调研活动。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据要求，组织党员走访企业</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>80</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家、家庭户</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3049</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">户，收集和梳理问题</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>192</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个，其中</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>96</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个问题录入网上平台后均已获得答复并反馈给被走访对象。我委接到平台流转问题</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>47</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">条，已办理</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>47</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">条。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">二是完善机关基层党组织建设。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">根据基层党组织设置要求，精心组织、扎实做好机关基层党组织选举、按期换届工作，三个党支部均完成了改选，一支党性强、作风实、业务精、服务优、评价好的党组织班子基本建成。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">三是不断加大服务企业力度。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">一年来，为企业</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">申报市级项目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>595</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个，申请扶持资金</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>4.25</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿元；积极协助企业向上争取国家、省、市级专项扶持政策等各个层面的优惠政策。截止目前，向上争取省级扶持资金项目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>118</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个，资金</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>7389</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万元；修订《昆山市工业企业转贷应急资金管理办法》，应急转贷资金合作银行已达</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>11</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家，累计发放转贷资金</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>5.7</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿元，惠及</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>57</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家企业，累计为企业节约融资成本超</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>898</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万元。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm">三、坚持全面从严治党，廉洁型党组织建设不断深化</SPAN><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">一是</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">明确目标任务，推进党风廉政建设。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据市委的决策部署和有关实施意见，结合本委党的建设实际，研究出台了市经信委党风廉政建设实施细则，明确了责任领导、责任科室，从严明政治纪律、推动责任落实、注重抓早抓小、强化作风建设、坚持惩防并举、加强队伍建设等方面抓好工作，把党的建设目标与经信工作目标统筹谋划，把党的建设列入机关日常绩效和年度考核的重要内容，确保党的建设贯穿于经信工作全过程，做到党的建设与经信工作同频共振、相互促进。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二是制定清单明责，压实落实</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">两个责任</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据上级对</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">两个责任</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">落实的检查考核内容，分别制定了</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年度《党委领导班子主体责任清单》、《领导班子成员责任清单》以及年度重点项目，<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: white">初步构建起了以清单引导任务、以手册记录过程、以台账查找差距的责任内容具体化、履责过程纪实化、工作管理台账化的管理体系，委机关党风廉政建设主体责任基本落实到位。</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三是<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: white">坚持挺纪在前，强化权力运行。</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">持之以恒认真贯彻中央</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">八项规定</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、省委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">十项规定</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、苏州市委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">十二项规定</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">和昆山市委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">十六项规定</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，并结合经信工作实际，认真开展</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">清风行动</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">专项督查活动，进一步规范</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三公</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">经费使用，规范招投标、物资采购和公务用车使用管理，严格公务活动纪律。<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: white">紧盯重要节点，强化监督检查，持续用力正风肃纪，反</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">四风</SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">向纵深推进，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">严格执行</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三重一大</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">集体决策制度。加大对重点科室、关键岗位和重要环节的风险防控，不断完善工作流程，确保权力在阳光下运行。坚持以工业经济专项财政补贴等为重点，着力解决财政资金规范使用、高效管理的问题，以规范和制约权力运行为核心，大力推行项目申报工作的网络平台标准化运作，着力打造运行安全、管理规范、使用有效、监督到位的评审机制。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2018</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年是贯彻党的十九大精神的开局之年，是改革开放</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>40</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">周年，是决胜高水平全面建成小康社会、实施</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">十三五</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">规划承上启下的关键一年。经信委党建工作总的要求是：坚持以习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想为指导，紧扣学习宣传贯彻党的十九大精神主线，把握纪念建党</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>97</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">周年和改革开放</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>40</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">周年两个时间节点，以</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">铸坚强堡垒、树经信形象</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">党建规范年为主题，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">突出严肃党内政治生活、强化党内监督，着力压实党建工作主体责任，全面加强市经信委机关党的思想、组织、作风、反腐倡廉和制度建设，抓基础立长远，抓规范促落实，抓典型创亮点，</SPAN><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">为建设生产先进的新昆山</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">提供坚强的政治、思想和组织保证。</SPAN><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">新的一年，经信委党建工作要坚持系统化思维、注重规律性把握，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">强化</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">五个坚持</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">，落实</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">四个要求</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">，实现新突破，取得新进展。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">五个坚持</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">即一要坚持学习为先，热爱学习、善于学习，更要学以致用、知行合一。二要坚持责任为重，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400; mso-fareast-language: #0400">把责任扛在肩上，勇于挑最重的担子，敢于啃最硬的骨头，善于接最烫的山芋</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">要坚持落实为基，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">弘扬实事求是作风，增强狠抓落实本领，察实情、说实话、谋实事、出实招、求实效，既要雷厉风行，更要久久为功，以钉钉子精神做实做细做精做好各项工作。四要坚持创新为要，突出目标引领、问题导向，强化对标找差、靶向思维，注重理念创新、机制创新、能力创新、文化创新。五要坚持清正为本，清清白白做人、干干净净做事、坦坦荡荡为官，不忘初心、牢记使命、保持敬畏、坚守底线，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">要对得起组织、对得起人民、对得起自己，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">构建亲清新型政商关系。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">四个要求</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">即一要旗帜鲜明讲政治。深入学习党的十九大精神，仔细研读领导讲话精神，善于领会领导的意图，善于找到工作的重点，善于想方法、出点子。二要持之以恒转作风。作风建设永远在路上。要对照形式主义、官僚主义</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">10</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">种新表现，找查摆问题、整改到位。三要全力以赴顾大局。全面理解大局意识、中心意识的丰富内涵，充分感受到经信人责任重大、使命光荣、任务艰巨。要时时处处以发展大局为重，把自己分管的工作放在昆山经济社会发展大格局中去思考、去把握、去推进。严格落实层层负责制，按照流程、规矩、层级推动工作。四要一着不让抓落实。要坚持系统化思维、注重规律性把握，遵循</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">切口小、实战性、闭环化、重创新</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400">的工作方法，共同为昆山争当强富美高新江苏排头兵的过程中，冲在前面、当好先锋，谱写新时代经信人绚烂的新篇章。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: #0400; mso-bidi-language: #0400"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">一、加强党性锻炼，强化政治建设</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、健全党内学习制度，落实各项学习任务。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">常态化制度化推进</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">两学一做</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">学习教育，严格按照上级部署安排，扎实开展</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">不忘初心、牢记使命</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">主题教育。认认真真、原原本本学习十九大报告、习近平总书记系列重要讲话读本和省、市党代会精神，认真学习经济发展新常态等有关知识，切实把思想和行动统一到党的十九大确定的目标任务上来，把智慧和力量凝聚到促进经信事业科学和谐发展上来。使全委党员干部理想信念更加坚定，精神状态更加振奋，创新作为更加自觉。主要工作任务：落实每月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">次的中心组学习；认真落实</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">三会一课</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">制度；组织各党支部每月安排</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">次学习讨论；组织全委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>2-3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">次专题讲座、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>1-2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">次学习征文和学习交流会；按照市委组织部等部门的轮训计划，安排党员干部参加轮训；认真落实党员日常教育和政治学习。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、提高履职能力水平，促进工作效率提升。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">进一步增强做好党建工作的政治责任感和时代使命感，党员领导干部要加强学习研究，把握时势趋势，把握大事要事，把握党员情况，充分发挥表率作用。全委党员同志要在工作中提高科学研判形势的能力、协调处理问题的能力、依法行政的能力，要在提高执行力上下功夫，在狠抓落实上比高低、看水平。主要工作任务：认真学习经信工作所需的政策法规、业务知识、专业技能，引导党员干部比学习、赛业务、亮本领。组织每月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">期的经信讲坛，围绕经信工作业务特点，邀请专家学者讲课，深入解读党建理论、业务工作知识或相关法律法规等。加强调查研究，为昆山经济发展积极献计献策。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、深入开展读书活动，努力建设书香机关。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">以弘扬社会主义核心价值观为主线，在全委干部职工中树立</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">终身学习、全员学习</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">的理念，引导干部职工多读书，读好书，做好人，为促进学习型机关建设营造良好氛围。各支部都要开展好书荐读活动，适时组织全委读书交流或</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">读好书</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">演讲比赛活动，形成</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">读好书、好读书</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">的良好氛围。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二、突出政治引领，提升整体水平</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、夯实战斗堡垒作用，提升党组织服务功能。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">机关各支部要自觉把工作放在大局中来谋划、来定位、来思考，进一步提升服务大局的能力；全委党员要倡导和树立心系群众、服务群众的良好风气，切实解决群众反映强烈的作风顽症，进一步提升服务群众的能力。主要工作任务：每季一次党委扩大会，组织学习，研究工作，听取意见。班子成员间要经常沟通思想，做到政治上关怀，生活上关注，营造良好的工作氛围。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、开展</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">勤走访、大调研、优服务</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">活动，强化党员干部服务意识。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">进一步深化和拓展</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">经信惠企</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">的品牌内涵，根据昆山经信委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">勤走访、大调研、优服务</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">活动的统一安排，党员干部要主动深入重点企业、重点区镇、重点项目等，宣传经信政策法规、了解企业发展现状、跟踪服务重大项目，有效帮助基层和企业解决发展难题。主要工作任务：继续关心帮扶</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">六个一</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">基层走访调研结对企业，以及挂钩联系区镇、企业，帮助企业了解规划、融资途径及相关政策，帮助企业拓展市场，努力适应服务对象的特点与需求。一如既往做好</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">六个一</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">基层走访调研结对帮扶及领导干部的阳光扶贫等工作。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、加强主题活动主阵地作用，推进和谐机关建设。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">倡导群众性健身活动，培养健康情趣，打造活力机关。主要工作任务：结合</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">书香机关</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">活动，组织读书、演讲、征文活动。结合重大纪念日，组织、歌咏、球类等比赛，努力营造健康生活、快乐工作的良好氛围。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三、突出固本强基，强化政治功能</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、夯实基层组织建设，力促工作上新台阶。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">认真贯彻执行党内民主集中制，坚持和完善党内生活制度，努力建设一支党性强、作风实、业务精、服务优、评价好的党组织班子。主要工作任务：着力抓好基层党组织建制、班子配备等工作。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、规范党内组织生活，加强党员教育管理。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">重视组织生活，适时开展适合党员特点的活动。组织好公开承诺、民主生活会、民主评议等活动，在活动中强化对党员的管理，增强党员意识和党性观念。主要工作任务：以</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">三会一课</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">微党课</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、党员活动日、党务公开活动日为主要载体，每月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">次组织生活。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、加大党风廉政建设力度，筑牢勤政廉政思想防线。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">认真抓好党风廉政建设宣传教育活动，通过教育使党员干部增强责任、廉洁意识，达到雷厉风行、求真务实、敢于碰硬、提高执行力的工作作风。进一步深化党务、政务公开内容，落实党务、政务公开要求，完善党务、政务公开制度，促进党务、政务公开经常化、制度化、规范化。严格落实党风廉政建设责任制度，坚持谁主管、谁负责的原则，建立班子成员</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">两个责任</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>””</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">的责任意识，认真开展党员领导干部述职述廉、个人重大事项报告等工作。主要工作任务：协助纪检组开展</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“5.10</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">思廉日</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>“12.5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">国际反腐倡廉日</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">活动，举办廉政党课、廉政教育基地参观、观看警示教育片、廉政短信、学习体会等活动，促进党风廉政建设经常性、常态化。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
